#: ../ddm-mx:954
#, sh-format
msgid ""
"Please remove with  <sudo nvidia-install --uninstall> and reboot if you wish"
" to proceed"
msgstr ""
"Ju lutemi, hiqeni me  <sudo nvidia-install --uninstall> dhe riniseni, nëse "
